Package cps.mouradalpha.components

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Broker
    The class Broker implements a component that provides ManagementCI , PublicationCI and NotificationCI services, it requires also ReceptionCI and NotificationCI services
    Message
    The class Message implements MessageI, it represents the message structure exchanged with different components in this project.
    MessageFilterExampleRectangle
    The class MessageFilterExampleRectangle implements MessageFilterI, it's an example of a filter used our demo.
    Publisher
    The class Publisher implements a component that requires ManagementCI and PublicationCI services
    PublisherPerformance  
    PublisherWithPlugin
    The class PublisherWithPlugin represent a publisher that use PublisherPlugin in order to perform publisher operations.
    Subscriber
    The class Subscriber implements a component that provides ReceptionCI services, and requires ReceptionCI services
    SubscriberPerformance  
    SubscriberWithPlugin
    The class SubscriberWithPlugin represent a Subscriber that use SubscriberPlugin in order to perform Subscriber operations.
    SubscriberWithPluginFiltered
    The class SubscriberWithPluginFiltered represent a Subscriber that use SubscriberPlugin in order to perform Subscriber operations and uses also MessageFilterExampleRectangle to filter messages.
    TestPublisherSubscriber
